snippet.title: Celeste 64: Fragments of the Mountain - Full Game Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a complete walkthrough of Celeste 64: Fragments of the Mountain, a game celebrating 6 years since the release of Celeste! In this video I collect some ribbons, strawberries and finish the game by reaching the Badeline.

Celeste Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2fGzfk5AS81kJcEV03VNfiiL_GIGwikI

Subscribe to not miss new videos! https://www.youtube.com/@MeneKV

https://twitter.com/MeneKV
https://www.tiktok.com/@menekv

#Celeste #Celeste64 #FullGame
